dct_title_s: Road and topographical map of Santa Clara County and part of Santa Cruz County
dct_alternative_sm: 1908 road and topographical map of Santa Clara County and part of Santa Cruz County
dct_description_sm: Compiled under the supervision of J.G. McMillan, County Surveyor.
Also shows ranchos, townships, county supervisor districts, and points of interest.
